		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Weapon (@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.vYEfz3IGHqR9krzS]{Greatsword}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.ZOyejSDAVAH74Z4u]{Longsword}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.poEXwYP4n9HdRzwm]{Rapier}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.NLDdf7iJt09G64Dg]{Scimitar}, or @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.equipment24.Item.phbwepShortsword]{Shortsword}) - Very Rare (Requires Attunement)</p><p><em>This polished blade pirouettes through the air under your direction.</em></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 30 ft (Self)</p><p>Toss the sword into the air. It hovers, flies up to 30 feet, and makes one attack against a creature within 5 feet of itself using your attack roll and adding your ability modifier to damage.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Properties</strong></p><ul><li><p>While the weapon hovers, you can use a Bonus Action each turn to move it up to 30 feet and attack one creature within 5 feet of it.</p></li><li><p>After the weapon makes four hovering attacks, it attempts to return to your hand; if you lack a free hand, it falls to the ground in your space.</p></li><li><p>If no unobstructed path leads back to you, it moves as close as possible and drops. It ceases hovering if you grasp it or if you end your turn more than 30 feet away from it.</p></li></ul><p>@Embed[Compendium.dnd5e.content24.JournalEntry.dmgFoundryRefere.JournalEntryPage.Ok4iCgD25ENgoRxE cite=false caption=false classes=\"hide-in-embed\"]</p>",
